OEM Cameo WLN-2206 ([https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=18314 see here]), Atheros AP81 based, similar to other Cameo manuf. models such as the [[TRENDnet TEW-652BRP V1.xR]], [[D-Link DIR-615 rev C1]] / [[D-Link DIR-615 rev C2]], and [[Encore ENHWI-N2]]
Atheros part numbers used include AR9130-AC1E, AR9102-AL1E, and AR8216-AH1E.
[http://web.archive.org/web/20100201175549/http://wiki.x-wrt.org/index.php/Trendnet_TEW-632BRP On the now-defunct x-wrt.org wiki] (via archive.org)
The power adapter included with the device is a '''JENTEC''' AF1805-A.
